es as he cast a friendly grin in Dantess' direction.  After a moment he stopped spinning the sword and entered his previous guard once more, about six feet from Dantess.  \"But I shall play your game, for you are the teacher.\"  Ralf nodded at the footprints, \"circles, yes I get it, now go on.\"", "link_list": [], "image_list": [], "html": "Ralf's feigned attack met a deflection, but one he expected."}}